query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(it1 mi mi_idx) NoNestLoop(it1 mi mi_idx it2) NoHashJoin(it1 it2 mi mi_idx t) NoHashJoin(it1 it2 mi mi_idx t ci) NoHashJoin(ci it1 it2 mi mi_idx t n) */ select min(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
min(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
min(t.title) AS movie_title
from info_type AS it1
inner join movie_info AS mi
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' AND mi.info IN ('Action',
'Drama',
'War',
'Thriller',
'Crime',
'Family')
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(producer)',
'(voice)',
'(uncredited)',
'(executive producer)')
inner join name AS n
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f';
